			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	Defence plan is meant so you have a fixed formation for the fleets selected in case of being attacked, which gives you a better chance of survival. Orders are assigned by left-clicking on the fleet and then right-clicking (for me anyway with the old java) and then choose the order to assign.<br />
Not sure what you mean by the last question, but if you raid someone and you raid a planet not from your cluster (check name of your home planet), you will need cruisers or larger to attack.<br />
Hope that helps.<br />
<br />
Beo			   <P align=right></P>
